# Environment

Copy `.env.example` to `.env.local` for local development.

```bash
RESEND_API_KEY=re_xxxxxxxx
CONTACT_TO_EMAIL=jtlhltd@gmail.com
CONTACT_FROM_EMAIL=JTLH LTD <hello@jtlhltd.com>
```

Requires a verified sending domain in Resend (`jtlhltd.com`). Without `RESEND_API_KEY`, the contact form returns 503.
